SECRET
No. 75/CF/52.
GOVERNMENT OF INDIA
CABINET SECRETARIAT
New Delhi, the 2nd May, 1956.
The undersigned is directed to inform Members of
the Council of Ministers that Shri V.K. Krishna Menon,
Minister Without Portfolio, will in addition to his
present duties, hold charge of the Ministry of Health
during the absence of Rajkumari Amrit Kaur, whe is
going abroad on the 17th May, 1956.
COPY NO.
ABC
(A.S. Gill)
for Secretary to the Cabinet.
All Members of the Council of Ministers.
tran

Commission, for information.
"KSG"
300 copies.

the Private Secretary to the Vice-President/the Special
Assistant to the Prime Minister/the Principal Private
Secretary to the Prime Minister, for information.
